<h2 id='verify-a-user-39-s-zpk'>Verify a user&#39;s zpk</h2>
<p>Check if the zpk is expired. The zpk is used to authenticate a user.</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Definition</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>GET https://api.zoom.us/v2/users/<span class="o">{</span>userId<span class="o">}</span>/zpk
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Request</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>curl https://api.zoom.us/v2/users/<span class="o">{</span>userId<span class="o">}</span>/zpk
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Response</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>200 OK
</code></pre></div>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Path Arguments</th>
<th>&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>userId <strong>required</strong></td>
<td>The user ID or email address</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Query Arguments</th>
<th>&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>type <em>optional</em></td>
<td>User zpk</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
